《魔界塔士 沙加》是史克威尔首部销量超过百万的游戏<ref name="Staff2009a">{{cite web |url=http://release.square-enix.com/news/j/2009/05/okooygzqf.html |title=「サガ2秘宝伝説 GODDESS OF DESTINY」 タイトルロゴ、発売時期決定、公式サイト正式オープンのお知らせ |author=Staff |publisher=Square Enix |date=2009-05-11 |accessdate=2009-06-01 |language=ja |archive-date=2011-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726151202/http://release.square-enix.com/news/j/2009/05/okooygzqf.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；在2003年3月31日时，Game Boy版在全球出货137万，其中日本115万<ref name="Ref_2004">{{cite web |url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/ir/e/explanatory/download/0404-200402090000-01.pdf#page=27 |title=February 2, 2004 - February 4, 2004 |date=2004-02-09 |accessdate=2008-03-01 |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] |page=27 |archive-date=2011-08-13 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60uXFn4oT?url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/ir/e/explanatory/download/0404-200402090000-01.pdf#page=27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。史克威尔很快又发行了两部Game Boy续作<ref name="Ref_u">{{cite web |url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/archive/saga2/ |title=Sa・Ga2 秘宝伝説 |language=ja |publisher=Square Enix |accessdate=2009-06-01 |archive-date=2011-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812053241/http://www.square-enix.com/jp/archive/saga2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Ref_v">{{cite web |url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/archive/saga3/ |title=時空の覇者 Sa・Ga3 ［完結編］ |language=ja |publisher=Square Enix |accessdate=2009-06-01 |archive-date=2011-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812053329/http://www.square-enix.com/jp/archive/saga3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并在其它平台销售后来的沙加游戏。日本版包装上的单眼怪成为了系列的吉祥物，并在续作中以名为“Mr. S”的角色登场<ref name="Parish2009">{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/do/blogEntry?bId=8988525&publicUserId=5379721 |author=Parish, Jeremy |title=Looking at SaGa 2 Again |work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |publisher=[[UGO_Networks|UGO Networks]] |date=2009-05-11 |accessdate=2009-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/610YkBRzf?url=http://www.1up.com/do/blogEntry?bId=8988525 |archivedate=2011-08-17 }}</ref><ref name="Ref_w">{{cite web |url=http://www.square-enix.co.jp/saga20th/index.html |title=SAGA生誕 20周年 |publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] |language=ja |accessdate=2009-06-04 |archive-date=2011-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110909051210/http://www.square-enix.co.jp/saga20th/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Game_Freak|Game Freak]]创办人[[田尻智|田尻智]]称，游戏潜在影响了后来Game Boy的[[口袋妖怪系列|口袋妖怪系列]]，称游戏带给他系统不止可以动作游戏的理念<ref name="Ref_x">{{cite web |language=ja |url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/nom/0007/taidan1/page02.html |title=Pokémon interview |publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]] |accessdate=2009-06-01 |archive-date=2012-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119204749/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/nom/0007/taidan1/page02.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

游戏获得媒体褒贬不一的评价。[[IGN|IGN]]称《魔界塔士沙加》为一款“有着复杂游戏系统和坚实原声的迷人RPG”，但对游戏难度和“过时”图形表示不满<ref name="IGN" />。德国游戏杂志《Power Play》给游戏打了78%，称赞作品作为Game Boy上的第一款角色扮演游戏，展示了平台的潜力<ref name="mobyrank" />。[[Allgame|Allgame]]称赞作品作为角色扮演游戏的优点，但批评游戏的高难度及缺乏方向感<ref name="allgame" />。《芝加哥论坛报》称游戏“在某些方面有点慢，然而，如同最终幻想，值得你忍耐”，是一次“不错的探索”<ref name="Johnathan1991">{{cite news |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1991-06-28/entertainment/9102270016_1_nastiest-places-magnification-screen-action-shooter/2 |title=Getting There May Be Most Of The Fun With Game Boys |accessdate=2010-06-06 |date=1991-06-28 |page=73 |newspaper=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]] |publisher=Tony W. Hunter |author=Johnathan, Carter and Chip Carter |archive-date=2012-07-08 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120708000026/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1991-06-28/entertainment/9102270016_1_nastiest-places-magnification-screen-action-shooter/2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的[[Retronauts|Retronauts]]称其游戏性继承了《[[最终幻想II|最终幻想II]]》，但接着又称直到其续作才正确提炼了系统相关内容；他继续称，超能力者和怪兽角色种族的随机性让游戏非常困难<ref name="Ref_y">{{cite podcast |url=http://www.1up.com/do/minisite?cId=3156908 |title=Retronauts |publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |host=Jeremy Parish |date=2009-05-14 |accessdate=2009-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/610Yp6crC?url=http://www.1up.com/do/minisite?cId=3156908 |archivedate=2011-08-17 }}</ref>。

其它文章对《魔界塔士 沙加》的反映更好。作者[[Jeff_Rovin|Jeff Rovin]]在《如何在Game Boy中获胜》一书中盛赞了作品，称其完全手动，并认为游戏是“Game Boy部队的高潮成就，也是同类中最好的游戏”，虽然其不如《[[塞尔达传说_(游戏)|塞尔达传说]]》复杂<ref name="Rovin1991">{{cite book |title=How to Win at Game Boy Games |last=Rovin |first=Jeff |authorlink=Jeff Rovin |year=1991 |publisher=[[Signet_Books|Signet Books]] |isbn=0-451-17446-1 |page=101}}</ref>。Siliconera的斯宾塞·伊普称其为他庆幸玩到的游戏，并将其称为打开他对故事性游戏思维的游戏，这点更甚于[[勇者斗恶龙|勇者斗恶龙]]等游戏，并在一定程度上导致了该网站的创建<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2011/11/24/siliconera-thanksgiving-special/ |title=Siliconera Thanksgiving Special |date=2011-11-24 |work=Siliconera |author=Staff |accessdate=2011-11-25 |publisher=CraveOnline |archive-date=2011-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111127013809/http://www.siliconera.com/2011/11/24/siliconera-thanksgiving-special/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1991年5月，《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》将游戏列为上年总体最佳Game Boy游戏的第三名<ref name="NP 1990">{{cite journal |journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] |publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]] |issue=24 |page=33 |title=Nintendo Power Awards |author=Staff|date=May 1991}}</ref>，并在1997年9月将游戏列为任天堂系统“最佳100”游戏的第70名，称其“忠于史克威尔的传统”<ref name="NP Top 200">{{cite journal |last=Staff |title=Nintendo Power's 100 Best Nintendo Games of All Time |journal=Nintendo Power |issue=100 |page=98|date=September 1997}}</ref>。1UP.com的杰里米·帕里什称游戏为Game Boy“必备”游戏之一及1989年最佳游戏之一，称其引入了和最终幻想系列不同的新理念，并称其为“凭借自身力量的非常棒的携带RPG”<ref name="Parish2009a">{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/do/blogEntry?bId=8987032&publicUserId=5379721 |publisher=[[UGO_Networks|UGO Networks]] |work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |accessdate=2009-11-17 |date=2009-04-28 |author=Parish, Jeremy |title=8-Bit Cafe: Game Boy Essentials, 1989 Edition |archive-date=2016-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409120946/http://www.1up.com/do/blogEntry?bId=8987032 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[GameDaily|GameDaily]]明确将其称为最终幻想相关Game Boy游戏，并称游戏提供了“数小时的角色扮演刺激，无论你是在牙医诊所 等待，还是在去祖母家的路上”<ref name="Workman2008">{{cite web |author=Workman, Robert |date=2008-01-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080228020505/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/retro-rewind-game-boy/189/?page=6 |archivedate=2008-02-28 |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/retro-rewind-game-boy/189/?page=6 |title=Retro Rewind: Game Boy |work=[[GameDaily|GameDaily]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |accessdate=2009-06-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。安德鲁·万登·裁范博希称游戏是日本角色扮演游戏中“最不寻常的”，将其叙事描述为“连接零散的经历，而非RPG类普遍认为的史诗般叙事类型”。因此美版中非玩家角色屏幕外的死亡感觉更“令人沉痛”，是[[Memento_mori|死亡象征]]的例子之一<ref>{{cite web|author=Andrew Vanden Bossche|date=May 19, 2010|title=Design Diversions: Memento Mori|publisher=GameSetWatch|url=http://www.gamesetwatch.com/2010/05/columndesign_diversions_moment.php|accessdate=2011-03-12|archive-date=2011-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711072230/http://www.gamesetwatch.com/2010/05/columndesign_diversions_moment.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而他还认为，怪兽种族系统违反直觉，正如常言怪兽的种族强调“旨在面临挑战，不能克服它们”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesetwatch.com/2009/06/design_diversions_bad_monster.php |date=2009-06-25 |accessdate=2011-09-30 |title=Design Diversions : 'Bad Monster, No Biscuit' |author=Andrew Vanden Bossche |publisher=GameSetWatch |archive-date=2010-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100820003429/http://www.gamesetwatch.com/2009/06/design_diversions_bad_monster.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《电子游戏月刊》、《Game Informer》、《Pocket Games》和[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]都表达了这种观点；后三者还将称游戏为最佳十五个Game Boy游戏之一<ref name="Pocket">{{cite journal |last=Staff |year=1999 |month=Summer/Fall |title=Top 50 Games |journal=Pocket Games |issue=1 |page=32}}</ref><ref name="gameinformer">{{cite journal |last=Staff |page=16 |title=The Top 25 Game Boy Games of All-Time |journal=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |issue=59|date=March 1998}}</ref><ref name="Staff1999">{{cite journal |last=Staff |year=1999 |title=Game Boy Pocket |journal=Electronic Gaming Monthly Buyer's Guide |issue=7 |page=55}}</ref><ref name="Davis">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/universal/gameboy50/sec3.html |title=VideoGames.com Presents the Top 50 Game Boy Games |author=Davis, Cameron |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2009-11-16 |archive-date=2010-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100720031240/http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/universal/gameboy50/sec3.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一些媒体还提到游戏难度和最终[[头目_(角色类型)|头目]]神的意义。《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》将其列为“史上最恶的47名电子游戏反派”的第37名，并称“你一定想知道开发商在给神多少[[生命值|生命值]]”<ref name="Staff2008a">{{cite web |work=GamePro |accessdate=2009-06-01 |date=2008-02-04 |url=http://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/210911/47_most_diabolical_video-game_villains_all_time?pp=1 |title=The 47 Most Diabolical Video-Game Villains of All Time |author=Staff |archive-date=2011-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814062225/http://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/210911/47_most_diabolical_video-game_villains_all_time/?pp=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1UP.com称战斗为“史诗”，认为角色队伍一起杀掉上帝是日本角色扮演游戏中反复出现主题之一<ref name="Kalata2007">{{cite web |title=Clash of the Cultures |url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=7&cId=3155815 |date=2007-01-08 |author=Kalata, Kurt |work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |publisher=[[UGO_Networks|UGO Networks]] |accessdate=2009-06-01 |page=8 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/610Z1A5vl?url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=7 |archivedate=2011-08-17 }}</ref>。《[[Comedy_Central_Presents|Comedy Central Presents]]》创办者喜剧演员杰基·凯山称，游戏最终战是“电子游戏有史以来最糟糕的”，并回忆和她如何试过用八个月击败头目<ref name="Ref_z">{{cite episode |title=Comedy Central Presents: Jackie Kashian |series=[[Comedy_Central_Presents|Comedy Central Presents]] |credits=Presenters: Jackie Kashian |network=[[Comedy_Central|Comedy Central]] |airdate=2003-02-28 |season=7 |number=4 }}</ref>。虽然最终头目很难，但却可以简单的用武器“链锯”直接杀死他。在2009年，史克威尔艾尼克斯战斗企划Nobuyuki Matsuoka通过在《[[最终幻想XIII|最终幻想XIII]]》中故意留给头目类似的弱点，表达了对这一事实的敬意<ref name="Square2010">{{cite book |title=ファイナルファンタジーXIII シナリオアルティマニア |publisher=Square Enix |author=Square Enix |language=ja |isbn=4-7575-2775-6 |date=January 2010}}</ref>。

